                            <comment id="314764" author="adilger" created="Tue, 5 Oct 2021 20:56:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this is virtually identical to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11608&quot; title=&quot;DoM2: inherited DoM component size is not limited&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11608&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11608&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="271511" author="tappro" created="Fri, 29 May 2020 10:23:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;yes, this should be fixed. As for &lt;tt&gt;dom_stripesize&lt;/tt&gt; param, I wouldn&apos;t make it another parameter but keep it the same with &lt;tt&gt;dom_stripesize_max_kb&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
